               <msContents class="#STM">
                  <summary><p>The <title xml:lang="ta">Kumarēcacatakam</title>, by Kurupāta Tācar (Zvelebil 1995, p. 387).</p>
<p>The text is incomplete. The manuscript stops short in U2, f25r, with the beginning only of v. 48, whereas in U2, f25v, unblackened, we find only the intetitle and the the first letters of the verse.</p>
<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (February 2021 and June 2021).</p>
<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p> </summary>
                  
